# aero-site repo ignores
# The tracked content of this repo is the website under site/ (plus .github/).
# Everything below either belongs to another repo, is a local build cache, or is
# a working/scratch doc that should not be committed here.

# --- Nested repo: the Aero wiki is its own repository (rymanov/aero-wiki),
#     the SSOT for product/eng/store/site/brand. It lives inside this working
#     tree for convenience but must NOT be added to aero-site. ---
aero-wiki/

# --- App source stub: the real Aero app source lives only on the Mac Mini
#     (~/dev/aero). This Aero/ folder is a partial, non-authoritative stub —
#     editing it here does nothing. Do not track it. ---
Aero/

# --- Local scratch / handoff / design / prompt docs kept at the repo root.
#     These are working notes, not shippable site content. Root-level markdown
#     only — site/**/*.md and aero-wiki/**/*.md are unaffected. If you ever want
#     a tracked root doc (e.g. a real README.md), add it with `git add -f`. ---
/*.md

# --- Build caches / editor / OS junk ---
.wrangler/
.obsidian/
.claude/settings.local.json
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
